{
  "texts": [
    "The experience layer: The excitement and resources the Metaverse has attracted are directly related to the realistic experiences it is positioned to offer.",
    "The Metaverse is made up completely of experiences.",
    "Gaming, social interactions, eCommerce, entertainment, and e-sports may all be revolutionized by the immersive and real-time features of a true Metaverse.",
    "• The discovery layer: This layer describes how app stores, search engines, review websites, and display advertising can help users find new experiences or platforms.",
    "Most discovery tools fall into one of two categories: inbound or outbound."
  ]
}